SummaryEnglish: Slice-of-life story about a group of four girls on the school tennis team. They rarely play tennis.

8.TitleEnglish: Jingle All the Way with Senpai

1.TitleEnglish: Once in a Lifetime with Senpai
1.SummaryEnglish: Teaching Yuri how to play tennis is harder than herding cats.

2.SummaryEnglish: Takamiya Nasuna has returned to play tennis, but first they have to harvest the court.

3.SummaryEnglish: Bando Marimo means well, but she has a soul of an old man... a perverted old man.

4.SummaryEnglish: Kanae has invited the club to her house... things get awkward from here.

5.SummaryEnglish: All jokes aside, Nasuno decides to get serious and play at her full strength!

6.SummaryEnglish: The girls enjoy a day at the pool by themselves.

7.TitleEnglish: From Russia with Love with Senpai

8.TitleEnglish: Born on the Fourth of July with Senpai
8.SummaryEnglish: Nasuno wants to create something "special" for her father's birthday.

10.SummaryEnglish: The showers at school are broken so the club visit the public baths.

12.SummaryEnglish: The club is finally back to practicing but when they lose their only ball...

1.SummaryEnglish: The four members of tennis club are asked to help with a bean throwing event by Kanae's cousin, who works at a nursery school. Concerned the children are frightened of her, Marimo receives advice from the principal, but...

2.SummaryEnglish: Kondo-san from the newspaper clubs asks to interview the tennis club. Can the excited upperclassmen properly show off the activities of the tennis club?!

3.SummaryEnglish: At Nasuno's suggestion, the four girls go on an overnight trip together. However, as expected, there's something strange about the method of transportation and lodging arranged by Nasuno...

4.SummaryEnglish: After finishing practice on their overnight trip and recharging themselves in the bath, the four girls hold a hot springs table tennis tournament. How will the gradually escalating battle end?

5.SummaryEnglish: On the final day of their trip, the tourist spot the manager told the girls about turns out to be a silver mine! And what event occurs on the bus on their way home...?

6.SummaryEnglish: When Nasuno suddenly declares she wants a pet, she and the other members head to the pet store where they find unbelievable animals!

7.SummaryEnglish: The day of the sports festival has arrived. Having entered a club relay race, the members come together to try to win, but...

8.SummaryEnglish: When Kanae becomes upset over her short stature, Nasuno takes her to a ranch. Will milking a cow make her taller!?

9.SummaryEnglish: One day, the four girls take on the base ball club with their right to use the tennis court on the line. Certain character appears to fill their roster, turning it into a white hot battle!

10.SummaryEnglish: At the bottom of the first inning with bases loaded and two outs, batter Kanae breaks out a certain pose! And finally, the conclusion!

11.SummaryEnglish: One night, a mysterious flying object crash lands at Marimo's house. From the dazzlingly bright light appears an alien who calls himself "Tomalin!"

12.SummaryEnglish: Kanae and Yuri go to an udon restaurant with coupons they received from Kondo-san. However, there's nothing ordinary about this udon restaurant!

1.TitleEnglish: The World is Not Enough with Senpai
1.SummaryEnglish: Nasuno-senpai takes everyone skiing. On what kind of course did the four skiing beginners end up?!

2.SummaryEnglish: When it starts pouring rain, everyone seeks shelter at Kanae's house. On their way home, Kanae is struck by a bolt of lightning and uses her superpower "Kana Kana Wave"...

3.SummaryEnglish: Nasuno is saved from a group of seemingly terrifying hooligans by a high school student named Yota. However, another group of assassins appears!

4.SummaryEnglish: At the suggestion of a long-haired Nasuno and short-haired Kanae, Yuri accompanies them to a salon. What NEW hairstyles does she see during her trip?!

5.SummaryEnglish: The group heads to the shrine for their first visit of the New Year. After drinking some amazake, Yuri runs out of control and things turn dire!?

6.SummaryEnglish: Nasuno's bakery is 300 million yen in debt?! The girls try coming up with a new menu for the reconstruction of the store, but...

7.TitleEnglish: The Merchant of Venice with Senpai
7.SummaryEnglish: A story of Yuri as a third year middle school student. After making it into Kameido High School, Yuri tries to join the tennis team, but...

8.SummaryEnglish: When Kanae's strings break the gang heads to a tennis supply store. The store stocks nothing but unusual strings. Which strings will Kanae choose?

9.SummaryEnglish: Yuri encounters the lingering spirit of her uncle at his funeral. Somehow her uncle takes control of her body, and...

10.SummaryEnglish: While Marimo is playing games at home, she is suddenly sucked into the game world through her TV. Will Marimo make it safely back to her own world?

11.SummaryEnglish: The national tennis tournament has begun! What secret strategy does Kanae use against the formidable Usagikame High?!

12.SummaryEnglish: The fearsome final exams are approaching. The girls gather at Kanae's house to study.

1.SummaryEnglish: When Marimo forgets her lunch at home, her freeloading alien roommate Tomarin comes to deliver it. The girls decide to show Tomarin around Kameido High School, but for some reason school's a little unusual that day...

2.SummaryEnglish: For some reason Kanae receives aquarium tickets from a man riding an elephant. The girls decide to go together, but the situation at the aquarium becomes increasingly inappropriate...

3.SummaryEnglish: Kondo-san of the school paper asks Yuri for help with investigating the legend of the cherry tree growing in the school yard. Apparently something strange happens to those who receive romantic confessions underneath the tree.

4.SummaryEnglish: Kanae and Yuri discuss watching the meteor show said to appear that night. They plan to gether on the roof of Nasuno's house, but... Will they be able to see the meteor shower?

5.SummaryEnglish: The swimsuit episode is finally here! Everyone is brimming with excitement as they enjoy the beach in a variety of ways, but...

6.SummaryEnglish: Yuri panics as the previous episode requires a sequel. Though the girls end up adrift at sea, Yuri wonders if the relaxed upperclassmen truly are just brave.

7.TitleEnglish: Enemy at the Gates with Senpai
7.SummaryEnglish: Yuri is shown paranormal photos at Udonko's shop. She tries to welcome home Udonko's older sister and is shocked to learn she's the ghost she once met at a funeral.

8.SummaryEnglish: Kanae travels to her grandmother's home in the middle of the Egyptian desert to visit her grandfather's grave. It seems her extraordinary behavior comes from her grandmother.

9.SummaryEnglish: Yota practices to prepare for a practice soccer match. Nasuno offers to be his training partner, but she makes a ridiculous suggestion to help him win the game.

10.TitleEnglish: Shaun of the Dead with Senpai
10.SummaryEnglish: Marimo and Tomarin walk through town in the blazing heat. Inside an air-conditioned electronics store, Marimo begins explaining human electronics to Tomarin, but...

11.SummaryEnglish: The girls are hanging out at a candy store in the middle of summer vacation. When Kanae suggests they do something special for summer vacation, they begin throwing around ideas.

12.SummaryEnglish: Nasuno and Marimo have tea at a cafe. When Nasuno says she wants to work a part-time job to learn more about society, Marimo begins passionately offering advice based on her one day of work at a pork bowl restaurant!

1.SummaryEnglish: The girls win tickets to a certain place is a shopping mall lottery. Their destination is overseas, and they begin preparing for their trip, but...

2.SummaryEnglish: The girls arrive in Cambodia. They go on a conventional sightseeing tour, visiting ruins and more ruins in a tuk tuk.

3.SummaryEnglish: Today is the cultural festival! Yuri's class is putting on a tuna dissection show. Yuri and Udonko begin crawling full speed ahead to check out the other class' attractions.

4.SummaryEnglish: After losing an obstacle course race in a sports festival long past, the tennis club is assigned to pick up garbage in the school's courtyard. Marimo comments on how ironic it is that society's garbage should have to pick up garbage, when...

5.SummaryEnglish: The girls decide to hold a takoyaki party to celebrate fall. When they realize they have none of the necessary ingredients, they go to the store to buy some.

6.SummaryEnglish: Udonko decides to do a story on the mysterious alien Tomarin. The jokes fly during the interview due to their surprisingly good chemistry.

7.SummaryEnglish: Kanae suddenly enters the classroom while spitting blood. Shocked and dismayed, Marimo cannot contain her anger when she sees her hurt friend. In her quest to avenger her friend, she becomes a goddess of revenge...

8.SummaryEnglish: Kanae suddenly enters the classroom while spitting blood. The lead-in is the same until this point, but don't let that bother you. The girls decide to scout out a rival school, but...?

9.SummaryEnglish: The girls decide to roast potatoes. A certain fellow probably knows the most about sweets, but that aside, things don't generally go well for the girls as they can't find kindling and fail to start a fire properly...

10.TitleEnglish: The Day After Tomorrow with Senpai
10.SummaryEnglish: Seasons turn, and winter arrives. As Yuri walks through town in the brisk air, with a sidelong glance to Marimo slipping across frozen puddles, she spots Kanae wearing a mask for once.

11.SummaryEnglish: This mallet and mortar have been passed down for generations.

12.SummaryEnglish: My grandma's in the hospital for Tommy John surgery.

1.SummaryEnglish: The upperclassmen of the Tennis Club have PE class outside on a cold day. After warming up with exercise moves of their own creation, they take on the high jump.

2.SummaryEnglish: Kanae needs a new phone, but the clerk at the store keeps offering her products that are definitely not phones. Will Kanae and Yuri leave the store with a phone that can actually make calls?

3.SummaryEnglish: With Valentine's Day just around the corner, Udonko and Yuri decide to make chocolate. However, it seems Udonko is very confused about what Valentine's Day and even chocolate are supposed to be.

4.SummaryEnglish: The cherry blossoms are blooming, and the girls decide to go flower watching. When they arrive at the park, Yuri notices they've brought a few friends with them.

6.SummaryEnglish: Udonko begs Yuri and Kanae for help with her family's udon business. They agree to help make udon at the shop and are taught the ins and outs of udon by a very special teacher.

7.SummaryEnglish: When Mika tears her ACL, Bobby asks the girls to take her place in his annual hero show. Yuri is unsure, but the other members enthusiastically agree to do it.

8.SummaryEnglish: Once upon a time, there was a girl named Cinderella who wanted nothing more than to attend the party at the castle. However, with 245 evil sisters intead of two, will she be able to attend the party and meet her prince?

9.SummaryEnglish: The girls decide to form a band to get more out of their youth. However, the discussion quickly reaches an unusually serious level with tons of realistic terminology thrown around.

10.SummaryEnglish: The team's annual "Practice Super Seriously Day" has arrived. While the girls do indeed practice something that resembles tennis, it's still a far cry from "serious practice."

11.TitleEnglish: Planet of the Apes with Senpai
11.SummaryEnglish: Marimo runs into Udonko, who is on her way to look for an unidentified flying object that crashed into a nearby park. While searching for the UFO, they meet up with Tomarin and Tanaka-san, who points them in the direction of some peculiar "playground equipment."

12.SummaryEnglish: Marimo and her friends are trapped on an alien planet when their spaceship breaks down. While searching for the rubber band they need to repair their ship's engine, they come across a strange domed structure. When they open the door, they find a shocking surprise waiting for them.

1.SummaryEnglish: Right off the bat, Kanae-senpai is slurping cup noodles at the bottom of a giant hole. In the heavily accented speech of a pioneer, she invites Yuri to climb down into the hole and help her dig...? The long-awaited seventh season has begun! We look forward to another great year of Tekyu!

2.SummaryEnglish: Kanae's grandmother moves back to Japan from Egypt for no reason. Yuri is invited to help pick fruit. Grandma, fruit, help pick. Okay?!

3.SummaryEnglish: "Summer vacation is almost over," Kanae remarks during the introduction. Yuri snaps back precisely, "This anime's seasons are totally random." And that anime, Tekyu, is about to start again! Yahoooo!!!!

4.SummaryEnglish: When Yuri and Marimo realize they're gaining weight, they decide to go on a diet. The naturally slim Kanae offers to coach them, but her advice is shaky at best. Will the girls be able to lose weight?

5.SummaryEnglish: Kanae and Marimo are hanging out at the park on a cold day. When a bear happens to wander by, they decide to question him about his hibernation habits, but the bear has some shocking answers for them.

6.SummaryEnglish: One day at school, Yuri suddenly hears Udonko's voice in her mind. Using her newfound telepathic powers, Udonko suggests they go bowling. With the rest of the Tennis Club in tow, Udonko leads them to the bowling alley which turns out to be located somewhere familiar to the group.

7.TitleEnglish: The Grand Budapest Hotel with Senpai
7.SummaryEnglish: When Kanae complains about the cafeteria's food, the new lunch lady challenges her to a school food showdown. Kanae accepts, but on the day of the event, she is sitting at the commentator's table, while participating in her place is an all too familiar face.

8.SummaryEnglish: When Yuri doesn't come to school one day, the third years ask Udonko where she is. When they learn she's home sick with a cold, they arrange a trip to visit her.

9.SummaryEnglish: When Yuri runs into Annenkov, she gets dragged into a mixer with Annenkov and her friends. However, no one would have expected the kind of men who show up and the disaster that befalls her in the bathroom.

10.SummaryEnglish: Yuri is shocked when the seniors of the tennis club suggest they practice with the tennis club of Usakame High, their rival school's team. Though their announcement initially brings tears of joys to her eyes, they're quickly replaced by her regular irritation when she realizes just how similar the two teams are.

11.SummaryEnglish: The tennis club is going camping! With baseball equipment, gold-plated RV, and not a single member with a driver's license, the girls are ready to go.

12.SummaryEnglish: Kanae comes up with a brilliant new way for the girls to practice. Will their new practice methods enable them to finally compete in and win the national tournament?

1.TitleEnglish: Lord of the Flies with Senpai
1.SummaryEnglish: Kondo needs help coming up with a subject to write on for the national school newspaper contest. Will the girls be able to help her write a contest winning article?

2.SummaryEnglish: The girls are exhausted after another hard day of everything but practicing tennis. They decide to get ramen to fill their empty stomachs.

3.SummaryEnglish: The girls are going to the beach... if they can even make it there. With so many problems plaguing their trip there, will there ever be a beach episode?

4.SummaryEnglish: The girls are enjoying themselves at the beach when calamity strikes. Is this the end of the Kameido tennis club?

5.TitleEnglish: The Super-Scary Super-Strange Files! Scariest Movie Ever with Senpai
5.SummaryEnglish: After a day at the beach, the girls head to an inn to spend the night. However, there is a foreboding air about the shadow looking in...

6.TitleEnglish: Night at the Museum with Senpai
6.SummaryEnglish: The girls are bored at school when Nasuno announces that she bought an art museum. They immediately head there to check out the art, but the objects on display aren't what they were expecting.

7.SummaryEnglish: The girls decide to have some fun playing an online RPG. Will their party amass a wealth of equipment and experience points or end in tragedy?

8.SummaryEnglish: Yuri wakes up one morning to discover she's inside Marimo's body. But when she gets to school, she finds another version of herself inside her own body. Who is who? Who is the real Yuri?

9.TitleEnglish: Once Upon a Time in America with Senpai
9.SummaryEnglish: It's Kanae's first year of high school. Discover the exciting adventure that led her and Nasuno to join the tennis club.

10.TitleEnglish: Once Upon a Time in China with Senpai
10.SummaryEnglish: The upperclassmen's flashback continues. With Kanae and Nasuno already on the team, next to join them is...

11.TitleEnglish: Enemy of the State with Senpai
11.SummaryEnglish: It's the day of the Kameido High Marathon and the tennis club is raring to go. When Kanae and Marimo show up with strangely muscular bodies, it's only the beginning of a typically atypical race.

12.SummaryEnglish: The girls discover their tennis net is ripped, but all the club's funds have been spent on sandbags. With no other choice, they decide to work for a day at a fried chicken restaurant, where they run into a shockingly unfamiliar face.

10.TitleEnglish: Battles Without Honor and Humanity with Senpai

12.TitleEnglish: The Sound of Music With Senpai
